  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nCurrently there is not much structure within the quo2 component library. It is a flat list of components.\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\n\r\nThere has been consensus among the dev and design team to have a 1-1 mapping of the components used to the Figma design categorisation. (Unless it makes sense for the component to live elsewhere)\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- Restructure the current component library in code to match the Figma mapping\r\n e.g \r\n ```\r\n src/quo2/components\r\n   |--/tags\r\n        |-- tag\r\n        |-- tags\r\n        |-- context-tags\r\n   |--/avatar\r\n        |-- ring\r\n        |-- user avatar\r\n        |-- group avatar\r\n   |--/switcher\r\n        |-- home-cards\r\n        |-- 1-1-message-card\r\n   ```\r\n- Restructure the quo2 component library in the app to match this structure too.\r\n- Add some documentation/ design decisions in the relevant location.\r\n\r\n## Future Steps\r\n\r\nEnsure future p.r's have components being added in a similar manner.\r\n",
